{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://docs.inspireui.com","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Multi-language, including RTL","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"FluxStore - Universal mobile commerce Flutter app for Magento, WooCommerce and Opencart","meta_description":"Fluxstore is universal app that fully integration with the Woocommerce, Mangeto and Opencart","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"fluxstore","toc":null,"keywords":["fluxstore","flutter app","fluxstore","Magento app","Woo Commerce app","Opencart app"]},"html":"<p>This section show how to config Language, Country Code, Symbol, Currency, Google font.</p>\n<p>Multi-language supports to change not only the UI but also the Products and Category content via <strong>WPML plugins</strong> (for WooCommerce version). Fluxstore also support RTL Arabic language and more.</p>\n<p>When installing, if you get issue, please go to <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-question/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Questions</a> or <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-issues/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Issues</a> to find the solutions.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*elmUADc6HzKE8Zuf9-BSRw.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>From version 1.7.x, there are more than 10 languages in the app: English, Vietnam, Japanese, Chinese, Indonesiana, Spanish, Arabic, Romanian, Turkish, Italian, German, Portuguese, Brazil, French...  You also can add/edit/delete languages.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/51a3e/0_3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.214285714285715%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"fluxstore-1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/efcfb/0_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/11053/0_3.png 200w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/1b42c/0_3.png 400w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/efcfb/0_3.png 800w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/d25cb/0_3.png 1200w,\n/static/ebc455df5cd1d8829b4ceb10495ed5fe/51a3e/0_3.png 1400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-adddeleteedit-language\"><a href=\"#how-to-adddeleteedit-language\" aria-label=\"how to adddeleteedit language permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to add/delete/edit language?</h2>\n<p>To add a new language, please follow step below:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <code class=\"language-text\">lib/l10n/</code> the folder and copy the existing files to make a new one (you may see there are many languages demo from the app). Let’s take adding the new French (fr) Language for example, the format should be <code class=\"language-text\">intl_fr.arb</code>. We suggest using the Android Studio with <strong><a href=\"https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/13666-flutter-intl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Flutter Intl</a></strong> when inputting new language to support auto-generating the WidgetsLocalizations file <code class=\"language-text\">lib/generated/i10n.dart</code>.</li>\n<li>For version 1.6.4 and earlier:  Create a new Language setting from the Profile screen by cloning new Card Widget from <code class=\"language-text\">lib/screens/language.dart</code> (make sure to create a new language flag image and save to <code class=\"language-text\">assets/images/country</code>).</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*jR-1gXQxpA-Z2r2nEg541g.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p><strong>To change/add/remove languages</strong>, from version 1.6.5 onwards, you need to modify these files: (make sure to create a new language flag image and save to <code class=\"language-text\">assets/images/country</code>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lib<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>common<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>tools<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dart <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> getLanguagesList\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lib<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>common<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>constants<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>images<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dart<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">set</span> a <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">language</span> flag image\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lib<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>l10n\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lib<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>config<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>config_xx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`xx`</span></span> is language<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lib<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>config<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>states<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> city<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> or province <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> the country<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/constants/images.dart</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ImageCountry</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String <span class=\"token constant\">GB</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/gb.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String <span class=\"token constant\">VN</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/vn.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String <span class=\"token constant\">JA</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/ja.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String <span class=\"token constant\">ZH</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/zh.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String <span class=\"token constant\">ES</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/es.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> String <span class=\"token constant\">AR</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'assets/images/country/ar.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>If got issues, when add new language, please refer <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-issues/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-issues/</a></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p>Wordpress Plugins required\nOn WooCommerce, to support for translating the product content (title, description..), it is required to install the following plugin:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>WPML 3.4 or above</li>\n<li>WPML String Translation 2.0 or above</li>\n<li>WPML Translation Management 2.2 or above</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/?source=post_page---------------------------\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce Multilingual</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpml-to-wp-api/?source=post_page---------------------------\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">WPML to WP API</a>: this API will support to change the product/title/category base on the select language from WPML plugin.</li>\n<li>Detailed document: <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/related-projects/woocommerce-multilingual?source=post_page---------------------------\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">click here</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-set-a-language-as-the-default-language\"><a href=\"#how-to-set-a-language-as-the-default-language\" aria-label=\"how to set a language as the default language permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to set a language as the default language?</h2>\n<p>Update the DefaultLanguage from <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config.dart</code> (or <strong>lib/common/config/general.dart</strong> for Fluxstore app from version 1.6.5 onwards).</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"default-country-code-symbol\"><a href=\"#default-country-code-symbol\" aria-label=\"default country code symbol permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Default Country Code, Symbol</h2>\n<p>Open <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config.dart</code> file and update the <code class=\"language-text\">DefaultCurrency</code> section. (For Fluxstore app, this const is moved to <strong>lib/common/config/general.dart</strong> from version 1.6.5 onwards).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const kAdvanceConfig = {\n  &quot;DefaultCurrency&quot;: {\n    &quot;symbol&quot;: &quot;\\$&quot;,\n    &quot;decimalDigits&quot;: 2,\n    &quot;symbolBeforeTheNumber&quot;: true,\n    &quot;currency&quot;: &quot;USD&quot;\n  },\n  ...\n};</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"currency-switcher\"><a href=\"#currency-switcher\" aria-label=\"currency switcher permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Currency Switcher</h2>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/0c9ce/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/efcfb/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/11053/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 200w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/1b42c/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 400w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/efcfb/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 800w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/d25cb/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 1200w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/22e61/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 1600w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/4b363/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 2400w,\n/static/87e57ac3a050b8805133a00434be0a50/0c9ce/fluxstore_currencies_inspireui_flutter.png 2880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>This feature is only available for WooCommerce version, below is required condiction to active this feature:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mstore-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">mstore-api</a> to latest version <strong>v1.5.4.</strong></li>\n<li>Add new setting from Manage Currencies from WPML plugin:</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/12478/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 36.77758318739054%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"IMG_1790fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/efcfb/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/11053/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 200w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/1b42c/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 400w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/efcfb/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 800w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/d25cb/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 1200w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/22e61/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 1600w,\n/static/52bae9da950e78fd389b1a71b98c8d1c/12478/fluxstore_currency_flutter_inspireui.png 2284w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the Fluxstore project, and update the <em>lib/common/config.dart</em>: (For Fluxstore app, this const is moved to <strong>lib/common/config/general.dart</strong> from version 1.6.5 onwards).</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const kAdvanceConfig = {\n  ...\n  &quot;Currencies&quot;: [\n    {\n      &quot;symbol&quot;: &quot;\\$&quot;,\n      &quot;decimalDigits&quot;: 2,\n      &quot;symbolBeforeTheNumber&quot;: true,\n      &quot;currency&quot;: &quot;USD&quot;\n    },\n    {\n      &quot;symbol&quot;: &quot;đ&quot;,\n      &quot;decimalDigits&quot;: 2,\n      &quot;symbolBeforeTheNumber&quot;: true,\n      &quot;currency&quot;: &quot;VND&quot;\n    }\n  ]\n};</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"country-settings\"><a href=\"#country-settings\" aria-label=\"country settings permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Country Settings</h2>\n<p>To limit the country list from the Delivery screen, open <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/config.dart</code> and update the DefaultCountry (From version 1.6.5 onwards, open <strong>lib/common/config/payments.dart</strong>). </p>\n<p>Example: if you would like to display on 3 countries, configure as below:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const List DefaultCountry = [\n  {\n    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Vietnam&quot;,\n    &quot;iosCode&quot;: &quot;VN&quot;,\n    &quot;icon&quot;: &quot;https://cdn.britannica.com/41/4041-004-A06CBD63/Flag-Vietnam.jpg&quot;\n  },\n  {\n    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;India&quot;,\n    &quot;iosCode&quot;: &quot;IN&quot;,\n    &quot;icon&quot;:\n        &quot;https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/41/Flag_of_India.svg/1200px-Flag_of_India.svg.png&quot;\n  },\n  {&quot;name&quot;: &quot;Austria&quot;, &quot;iosCode&quot;: &quot;AT&quot;, &quot;icon&quot;: &quot;&quot;},\n];</code></pre></div>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/d86fc/default-shipping.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 53.99159663865546%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-06-11 at 09.49.05\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/efcfb/default-shipping.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/11053/default-shipping.png 200w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/1b42c/default-shipping.png 400w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/efcfb/default-shipping.png 800w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/d25cb/default-shipping.png 1200w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/22e61/default-shipping.png 1600w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/4b363/default-shipping.png 2400w,\n/static/363b05d8fb7362b81b7cf2c307ede569/d86fc/default-shipping.png 2856w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> ⚠️ Note: To update <strong>the States</strong> list of your country, add new state file. E.g.: to display State/Province for India, add the state file below:</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/4efbd/state.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 54.138702460850105%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/efcfb/state.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/11053/state.png 200w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/1b42c/state.png 400w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/efcfb/state.png 800w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/d25cb/state.png 1200w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/22e61/state.png 1600w,\n/static/a8a67ce237545fb4a0d2dd09eaddbe41/4efbd/state.png 1788w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"load-google-font-per-language\"><a href=\"#load-google-font-per-language\" aria-label=\"load google font per language permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Load Google Font per language</h2>\n<p>Flutter 1.2.x come with powerful Google Font library, you can load any font from google font and load to your app dynamically without downloading to the assets folder.</p>\n<p>If you add more languages to the app and would like to change the font family, go to <code class=\"language-text\">lib/common/constants.dart</code> (From version 1.6.5 onwards, go to <strong>lib/common/config/fonts.dart</strong>)</p>\n<p>Example: add new <code class=\"language-text\">fr</code> language with <strong>Lato</strong> font:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">///Google fonts<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//fonts.google.com/\nTextTheme kTextTheme(theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> String language) <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  switch (language) <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    case 'vi'<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      return GoogleFonts.montserratTextTheme(theme);\n    case 'ar'<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      return GoogleFonts.ralewayTextTheme(theme);\n    case 'fr'<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      return GoogleFonts.latoTextTheme(theme);\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      return GoogleFonts.ralewayTextTheme(theme);\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nTextTheme kHeadlineTheme(theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>language = 'en'<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>) <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  switch (language) <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    case 'vi'<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      return GoogleFonts.montserratTextTheme(theme);\n    case 'ar'<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      return GoogleFonts.ralewayTextTheme(theme);\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      return GoogleFonts.ralewayTextTheme(theme);\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>🗳 <strong>Coding Guide</strong>: Make sure the spacing align is correct.</p>\n<p>Note: When installing, if you get issue, please go to <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-question/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Questions</a> and <a href=\"https://docs.inspireui.com/fluxstore/common-issues/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Common Issues</a> to get Customer key, Consumer secret,... and to see the list of common issues and solutions to fix it.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-language/"},"timeToRead":6,"excerpt":"This section show how to config Language, Country Code, Symbol, Currency, Google font. Multi-language supports to change not only the UI but…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/Data/Projects/web/inspireui-document/content/fluxstore/multi-language.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/fluxstore/multi-language/"}}